'''Olivia Hussey''' ([[April 17]], [[1950s#1951|1951]] &ndash; [[December 27]], [[2024]])<ref name="SFC" /> was an actress who provided the voice of [[Kasan Moor]] in [[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron (video game)|''Star Wars: Rogue Squadron'']], [[All Terrain Anti-Aircraft|AT-AA]] Driver and [[Abridon/Legends|Abridon]] Refugee 2 in ''[[Star Wars: Force Commander]]'', and [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Yuon Par]] in ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''.

